The '''Naos sharptooth''' was a pink-fleshed fish native to [[Naos III/Legends|Naos III]]. It spawned only in the coldest months of the already-cold year. Exportation of the sharptooth - a massively expensive delicacy across [[The galaxy/Legends|the galaxy]] - was the prime and only export of the moon. Other than the occasional rich tourist fisherman, all sharptooth business was controlled by the [[Naos III Mercantile]].

